Class Shift

java.lang.Object
models.Shift
public class Shift extends Object
The Shift class represents a work shift for an employee. It contains details such as the shift's unique ID, start time, end time, and the date of the shift. This class provides getter methods to access shift details, and it overrides the toString() method to return a string representation of the shift.
